NAME
    Scalar::DDie - Defined or die.

SYNOPSIS
        use Scalar::DDie;

        say ddie($var);

DESCRIPTION
    Scalar::DDie checks the scalar value. If the value is not defined then
    it throw exception. Just return value otherwise.

